1.0.name: wordpress/artblog
1.0.description: Artblog is a WordPress theme for artists. An artist theme is in my opinion a theme, that is simple, so it does not draw to much attention. Artists ofen have a lot of images showing their art. With a simple artist theme, as Artblog, those images is the main focus. Artblog comes with the languages: English, Danish, German, Italian and French. .
